# App builder pipeline

When the user is building an app (see `APP_SPEC.md`):

1. **Plan** — Use `app-planner` if no milestone is `in_progress`.
2. **Build** — Use `app-builder` for exactly one milestone.
3. **Review** — Use `safe-code-improver` on changed files.
4. **Test** — Use `app-tester` to verify acceptance criteria.
5. If tester returns `NEEDS_FIX`, use `app-builder` once more (max 2 fix loops), then stop and report.

Never skip testing. Never implement multiple milestones in one session unless the user explicitly asks.
